subject: Football
lead_paragraph: Jay Cutler threw a go-ahead 5-yard touchdown pass to Earl Bennett in the fourth quarter, Matt Forte ran for 133 yards and the Chicago Bears defeated the Philadelphia Eagles, 30-24.
